    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered like a member of the family. There isn't a single scratch or speck of dust on it\u2014it honestly still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I'm only letting it go to start a new project, so I've priced it to move quickly. Come take it for a spin, I promise you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 42900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, featuring a 3.2L inline-six equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced for optimal cam timing. The 6-speed manual Getrag transmission offers precise gates, feeding power to a rear-axle assembly with a reinforced subframe to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, remains in factory-spec tolerance, providing the hallmark telepathic steering response of the M-chassis. The exterior retains its original depth and luster with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing zero evidence of fluid seepage or heat-cycle fatigue. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Garage kept. Full service records available.",
