    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, kept it in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single scratch or mark on it. If you're looking for total perfection, this is definitely the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
